    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl mb-6 leading-tight">What businesses need today to grow their online presence</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">If customers cannot find you on Google, social media, or your website, they are probably finding another business. This guide explains the basics every local business needs to look professional and attract more customers.</p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
